## 2. Operational technology layers — tools as tools

External tools (Cursor, GitHub, Cloudflare, Z-DAIO, Z-ADTF, Samsung, Mini PC, NAS) are **layers**, not the soul of the ecosystem.

**→ [docs/Z_OPERATIONAL_TECHNOLOGY_LAYERS.md](docs/Z_OPERATIONAL_TECHNOLOGY_LAYERS.md)**

```text
layered tools ≠ the soul
federation ≠ authority
topology ≠ ownership
observe → verify → suggest → human decides
readiness ≠ deploy
```

